<Paragraph Style="{DynamicResource HeaderParagraphStyle}">This sample demonstrates how a PDF document can be protected with user and owner passwords. Essential PDF has support for 40-, 128- and 256-bit encryption and the ability to restrict the following permissions: </Paragraph>
<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Allow Edit Content</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Allow Copy Content</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Allow Edit Annotations</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Allow Accessibility Copy Content</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Allow Assemble Document</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Allow Print</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Allow Full Quality Print</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

